Keep the bar open.

1:13:35.759 --> 1:13:38.065
You look like
you can use it.

1:13:53.559 --> 1:13:56.257
JACK: What did she do
after she killed Benny?

1:14:00.392 --> 1:14:03.439
Jesus Christ! What the fuck
are you doing here?

1:14:03.569 --> 1:14:05.528
I'm here because of you.

1:14:12.578 --> 1:14:13.492
Do you like it?

1:14:14.754 --> 1:14:15.929
Jack, Jack, stop!

1:14:16.060 --> 1:14:17.844
[tires screeching]

1:14:20.368 --> 1:14:21.500
[horn honks]

1:14:21.631 --> 1:14:23.371
Jack, you could have
killed us both!

1:14:23.502 --> 1:14:25.678
Tell me everything you know,
and I'll take you to the money.

1:14:25.809 --> 1:14:27.114
Fuck the money!

1:14:31.510 --> 1:14:34.426
Look, it's not safe
for you here!

1:14:34.557 --> 1:14:36.384
I'm worried about you, Page!

1:14:36.515 --> 1:14:40.127
These people, Zaney, Karim,
you have no fucking idea!

1:14:40.258 --> 1:14:43.957
You're worried about me?
Why'd you put a gun to my head?

1:14:44.088 --> 1:14:46.438
Look, I'm sorry, okay?

1:14:48.832 --> 1:14:51.487
I'm losing my fucking mind here.

1:14:53.010 --> 1:14:55.491
Will you please
just get back in the car?

1:14:57.405 --> 1:14:58.711
Please.

1:15:06.632 --> 1:15:07.981
JACK: I realize there are
people out there

1:15:08.112 --> 1:15:09.809
who don't much care about me.

1:15:09.940 --> 1:15:12.464
About us, Page.

1:15:12.595 --> 1:15:15.380
So from now on,
I'm gonna protect you.

1:15:15.511 --> 1:15:17.774
PAGE: How will you
protect me, Jack?

1:15:17.904 --> 1:15:20.385
JACK: Look, when this
is all sorted,

1:15:20.516 --> 1:15:22.430
I'm gonna start fresh.

1:15:22.561 --> 1:15:25.129
Australia.

1:15:25.259 --> 1:15:26.478
You should come too.

1:15:34.747 --> 1:15:36.009
Here.

1:15:36.140 --> 1:15:37.663
Merci.

1:15:43.887 --> 1:15:45.932
I want the same, you know.

1:15:46.063 --> 1:15:49.545
Did you tell him
about the money?

1:15:52.896 --> 1:15:55.028
Okay, forget it.
I'll deal with it.

1:15:55.159 --> 1:15:57.030
Tell me about London.

1:16:04.255 --> 1:16:05.996
She put me there.

1:16:08.912 --> 1:16:11.392
I had no idea.

1:16:11.523 --> 1:16:12.916
Ronny?

1:16:15.005 --> 1:16:17.224
So we both lost her.

1:16:20.097 --> 1:16:23.491
Maybe she had more to lose
than either of us.

1:16:24.580 --> 1:16:26.494
I just need a minute.

1:16:31.891 --> 1:16:35.547
JACK: I overheard  a conversation, long forgotten.

1:16:35.678 --> 1:16:38.332
Couldn't make sense of it
at the time.

1:16:38.463 --> 1:16:40.465
But now...

1:16:40.596 --> 1:16:43.903
[speaking French]

1:16:53.217 --> 1:16:55.306
- Okay?
- Okay.

1:16:57.177 --> 1:16:59.223
VERONIQUE: You think this is
all about the money?

1:16:59.353 --> 1:17:00.877
Poor Jack.

1:17:03.444 --> 1:17:05.142
[distant gunshot]

1:17:12.062 --> 1:17:13.193
Page?

1:17:29.732 --> 1:17:32.560
Don't let him hurt me.

1:17:32.691 --> 1:17:33.692
[gunshot]

1:17:41.047 --> 1:17:43.746
PAGE: Zaney says
you're sitting on a fortune.

1:17:43.876 --> 1:17:46.226
ZANEY: I'm not the low-life
you think I am.

1:17:46.357 --> 1:17:47.314
[horn honks]

1:17:57.716 --> 1:17:58.935
I'm looking for Zaney.

1:17:59.065 --> 1:18:01.589
Oh, hasn't been in yet.

1:18:01.720 --> 1:18:03.722
Are you sure
he's not here, Tom?

1:18:03.853 --> 1:18:05.593
His van's outside.
The door's open.

1:18:05.724 --> 1:18:06.986
Lots of people all day.

1:18:07.117 --> 1:18:10.381
He's never usually late
like this.

1:18:11.469 --> 1:18:12.949
Any message?

1:18:14.254 --> 1:18:16.909
GRANT: Jack, we need to talk.

1:18:17.040 --> 1:18:19.738
Lane's alive.  He's got that picture of Ronny,

1:18:19.869 --> 1:18:21.609
the one you said
the girl stole.

1:18:21.740 --> 1:18:23.873
Holla back, yeah? ASAP.

1:18:29.574 --> 1:18:31.750
This is Grant. Leave a message. [beep]

1:18:31.881 --> 1:18:33.534
JACK: Grant,
for Christ's sake, call me.

1:18:33.665 --> 1:18:35.188
It's him.

1:18:35.319 --> 1:18:38.104
- [phone buzzing]
- Time to perform, Fleet.

1:18:44.807 --> 1:18:46.634
Fleet, what's going on?
Is Grant there to see you?

1:18:46.765 --> 1:18:49.333
Your friend's disappeared.
Things are going crazy here.

1:18:49.463 --> 1:18:51.335
If Karim's resurfaced,

1:18:51.465 --> 1:18:54.120
it's only a matter of time
before he finds you.

1:18:54.251 --> 1:18:56.296
Someone on your end
must have tipped him off.

1:18:56.427 --> 1:18:58.124
But you've gotta tell me
where you are.

1:18:58.255 --> 1:18:59.343
Hey!

1:18:59.473 --> 1:19:01.519
Jack, are you there?

1:19:01.649 --> 1:19:03.564
I need to talk to you.

1:19:03.695 --> 1:19:04.696
Hey!

1:19:07.177 --> 1:19:08.656
Zaney!

1:19:12.138 --> 1:19:13.270
Zaney!

1:19:15.185 --> 1:19:16.577
Zaney!

1:19:26.022 --> 1:19:27.632
Zaney.

1:19:28.807 --> 1:19:29.808
Hey!

1:19:29.939 --> 1:19:31.854
Come here, you little prick!

1:19:31.984 --> 1:19:34.770
Mr. Leyton, what's going on?
What is this?

1:19:34.900 --> 1:19:36.641
Don't give me
that "Mr. Leyton" shit.

1:19:36.772 --> 1:19:37.816
You know who I am.

1:19:42.212 --> 1:19:45.084
I'm gonna kill Karim, but first,
I'll fucking kill you.

1:19:45.215 --> 1:19:46.694
Should've let Page
out of this, Zaney.

1:19:46.825 --> 1:19:48.435
[gun cocks]

1:19:48.566 --> 1:19:50.437
It's not me she's afraid of.
It's you.

1:19:50.568 --> 1:19:52.178
The fuck does that mean?

1:19:52.309 --> 1:19:56.052
Please, please, it's me,
Steinjo.

1:19:56.182 --> 1:19:57.793
Why are you doing this? Why?

1:20:09.630 --> 1:20:12.808
You're fucking psycho, Leyton!
What you trying to prove?

1:20:14.766 --> 1:20:16.681
You come to my bar every day
with that silly dog

1:20:16.812 --> 1:20:18.291
and try to impress Angela.

1:20:18.422 --> 1:20:20.076
- But guess what.
- Aww...

1:20:20.206 --> 1:20:21.947
- Isn't he gorgeous?
- She.

1:20:22.078 --> 1:20:25.298
She only cares about the dog.
She just fucking likes the dog!

1:20:25.429 --> 1:20:26.865
I'm just...

1:20:26.996 --> 1:20:28.475
[mutters]

1:20:29.563 --> 1:20:31.261
Page, Steinjo...

1:20:31.391 --> 1:20:35.874
Zaney, Ronny, Page, Ronny...
[echoing]

1:20:40.400 --> 1:20:42.402
ANGELA: Are you okay?
STEINJO: He's got a fucking gun!

1:20:42.533 --> 1:20:44.100
Oh, my God! What?

1:20:44.230 --> 1:20:45.753
Okay, go, go.

1:20:47.016 --> 1:20:49.366
JACK: This can't be happening.

1:20:49.496 --> 1:20:50.802
Page!

1:20:53.631 --> 1:20:56.025
Who is it, Page?

1:20:56.155 --> 1:20:58.505
Who's gonna hurt you?

1:20:58.636 --> 1:21:00.072
Page!

1:21:06.731 --> 1:21:07.950
Page!

1:21:10.082 --> 1:21:11.344
Page!

1:21:18.003 --> 1:21:19.222
Ronny?

1:21:58.783 --> 1:22:00.437
[cocks shotgun]

1:22:00.567 --> 1:22:02.569
Don't let him hurt me.

1:22:04.180 --> 1:22:05.485
[gunshot]

1:22:07.444 --> 1:22:08.749
KARIM: Where's my money, Jack?

1:22:08.880 --> 1:22:10.229
I wanna see my wife first.

1:22:10.360 --> 1:22:11.883
Just get it done and get out.

1:22:12.014 --> 1:22:13.537
Let's see the money first.

1:22:26.680 --> 1:22:27.812
Don't let him hurt me.

1:22:27.943 --> 1:22:28.856
JACK: Ronny, move!

1:22:33.644 --> 1:22:35.254
[tires screeching]

1:22:58.669 --> 1:22:59.713
I killed her.

1:23:02.064 --> 1:23:03.065
She's dead.

1:23:06.024 --> 1:23:09.854
[horn honking]

1:23:09.985 --> 1:23:11.029
[grunts]

1:23:30.005 --> 1:23:31.441
[sniffles]

1:23:34.966 --> 1:23:38.100
[sobbing]

1:24:30.152 --> 1:24:32.545
ANNOUNCER: This is Buck,
laid off for Harry Page.

1:24:32.676 --> 1:24:34.982
Crosses Goode, Murdoch sweeps.

1:24:35.113 --> 1:24:37.115
Jack Stracken scores!

1:24:41.772 --> 1:24:44.079
ANNOUNCER:
Harry Page, Murdoch...

1:24:47.517 --> 1:24:49.606
FLEET: Jack.

1:24:49.736 --> 1:24:52.348
JACK: Fleet,
I remember everything.

1:24:52.478 --> 1:24:54.001
Where are you, Jack?

1:24:55.786 --> 1:24:58.093
Norway. Trondelag.

1:25:00.095 --> 1:25:02.358
Great.

1:25:02.488 --> 1:25:04.969
I'll send someone.

1:25:44.400 --> 1:25:45.401
FLEET: Jack?

1:25:48.578 --> 1:25:50.493
Jack, are you all right?

1:25:59.458 --> 1:26:01.330
Are your friends
coming to say hello?

1:26:01.460 --> 1:26:05.029
For fuck's sake, Jack,
it's me.

1:26:07.336 --> 1:26:09.555
Why don't you just
give the money back?

1:26:09.686 --> 1:26:11.731
Fuck! Don't blow this up!

1:26:16.780 --> 1:26:18.085
[screams]

1:26:18.216 --> 1:26:20.131
[gunshots]

1:27:06.482 --> 1:27:08.484
I killed the decoy.

1:27:08.614 --> 1:27:10.529
Which means...

1:27:36.903 --> 1:27:38.383
[coughing]

1:27:38.514 --> 1:27:40.777
Come on out, Jack,
before you burn!

1:27:40.907 --> 1:27:42.779
Money's in here with me, Lane!

1:27:42.909 --> 1:27:44.868
Why don't you
come and get it?

1:27:44.998 --> 1:27:47.349
KARIM: It has never been
about the money, Jack!

1:27:47.479 --> 1:27:49.264
It's the principle!

1:27:52.484 --> 1:27:54.486
You think I don't know that,
you sick fuck?

1:27:56.183 --> 1:27:57.881
Second-rate player
steals your fucking queen,

1:27:58.011 --> 1:27:59.622
you just don't take it.

1:27:59.752 --> 1:28:02.538
KARIM: That queen came running
right back to me, Jack!

1:28:02.668 --> 1:28:03.930
Did she?

1:28:04.061 --> 1:28:06.019
You killed
an innocent girl, Jack.

1:28:06.150 --> 1:28:08.674
You set that whole thing up just
to see me suffer, didn't you?

1:28:08.805 --> 1:28:11.373
Keep telling yourself that
if that makes you--

1:29:26.317 --> 1:29:29.015
[panting]

1:30:39.608 --> 1:30:41.914
[gagging]

1:31:39.842 --> 1:31:40.843
[gunshot]

1:31:50.766 --> 1:31:54.639
Nothing in life becomes so quiet
like the leaving of it.

1:31:54.770 --> 1:31:56.946
Eh, Jack?

1:31:57.076 --> 1:32:00.776
That's the look
I wanted to see in London.

1:32:00.906 --> 1:32:02.255
Abject failure.

1:32:02.386 --> 1:32:04.475
Now you know how it feels.

1:32:04.606 --> 1:32:05.520
[gunshot]

1:32:10.263 --> 1:32:11.656
Vee.

1:32:11.787 --> 1:32:14.790
Don't call me that.
You know I hate it.

1:32:16.574 --> 1:32:18.881
You thought I enjoyed
fucking you

1:32:19.011 --> 1:32:20.883
if I wasn't getting
my football club in return?

1:32:22.319 --> 1:32:23.494
[groans]

1:32:23.625 --> 1:32:28.281
Ridiculous men.
All money, sex, and ego.

1:32:30.153 --> 1:32:32.677
Can you walk?

1:32:32.808 --> 1:32:34.287
[seagulls squawking]

1:32:34.418 --> 1:32:35.375
[coughs]

1:32:42.818 --> 1:32:46.386
Veronique, I told myself
you were dead.

1:32:46.517 --> 1:32:51.304
And I told myself
that at least you were alive.

1:32:55.918 --> 1:32:57.876
I needed more, Jack.

1:33:08.495 --> 1:33:10.106
Split it, Jack.

1:33:12.499 --> 1:33:14.937
Don't look at me like that.

1:33:15.067 --> 1:33:16.939
You wouldn't take care of me,

1:33:17.069 --> 1:33:20.551
so I went back to him
and made a deal.

1:33:20.682 --> 1:33:22.988
He wanted to see you
with nothing.

1:33:23.119 --> 1:33:25.425
So you use a girl.

1:33:25.556 --> 1:33:27.863
Would you rather
have killed me?

1:33:27.993 --> 1:33:31.170
You should have stayed hidden.

1:33:31.301 --> 1:33:33.651
And sending Grant
was a mistake.

1:33:33.782 --> 1:33:34.957
Yeah.

1:33:41.746 --> 1:33:45.576
So what do we do
about the money?

1:33:48.666 --> 1:33:50.581
The club is all yours now.

1:34:03.246 --> 1:34:04.943
[motor starts]

1:34:11.210 --> 1:34:12.690
What was her name?

1:34:12.821 --> 1:34:14.736
What difference does it make?

1:34:17.608 --> 1:34:20.567
[motor revs]

